{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":null,"total_pages":1,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2013-11-28T00:50:47Z","content":"I have witnessed first hand the lack of care given to our seniors in nursing homes.  I have been extremely frustrated trying to get any results with the nursing home in question.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Angela Betker","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71213659"},{"created_at":"2013-12-01T03:06:19Z","content":"It is foolish to think that as we get older, we need less resources to take care of us. It is the opposite and standards must be established.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cheryl Netterfield","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71610051"},{"created_at":"2013-11-28T15:18:49Z","content":"because the second most vulnerable element of our society are abused on an ongoing basis","like_count":0,"author_name":"Guy Baril","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71299823"},{"created_at":"2013-12-01T01:45:36Z","content":"People are living longer than ever and the baby boomer tsunami is coming.  A strategic plan needs to be developed and executed before we reach a chaotic crisis.  My parents and family are living this nightmare now.  My condolences to the Alexander family. I pray something powerful comes as a result of this tragedy.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Margaret Zed","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71606999"},{"created_at":"2013-11-28T21:42:05Z","content":"It is important to me because one day I may be in the same position and would like to know that i am in a safe and caring environment and not have to fear for my life as i live out my life.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ericka Jathan","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71355170"},{"created_at":"2013-11-27T23:57:26Z","content":"I am aging. I want to be well taken care of as I age.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jackie Cohen","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71208072"},{"created_at":"2013-11-30T13:28:32Z","content":"My Father-in-law is Frank Alexander and he was killed by another patient in a nursing home in Manitoba","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandra Alexander","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71548315"},{"created_at":"2013-11-28T12:47:39Z","content":"As a nurse in a nursing home, I've seen violence between patient, I've been hit by a patient, and saw my mother in a nursing home also. Very understaffed and under trained workers.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cathy Danyluk","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71279639"},{"created_at":"2013-12-01T01:07:01Z","content":"As the baby boom moves its way through the need for specialized services for dementia and Alheimer's, an overarching startegy is needed.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tom Dercola","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71605346"}]}